  "title": "AutoCAD Drafter (West, 5 Days, $4.2k)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:<br />• Prepare production drawings to support ship building design and construction.<br />• Produce schematic (structural and piping), construction and as-built drawings.<br />• Coordinate closely with project leads on priority updates.<br /><br />Requirements:<br />• Diploma holder with 2 years experience in ship piping systems and outfitting design<br />• Proficient in AutoCAD (2D & 3D)<br />• Singaporean only need apply<br /><br /><strong>Please submit your resume in MS Word format to </strong><a href=\"mailto:sunnie@united-personnel.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>sunnie@united-personnel.com</strong></a></p><p>Please remember to include your<br />1) Recent photo<br />2) Current salary & Expected salary<br />3) Notice period</p><p><strong>UNITED PERSONNEL SERVICES</strong><br />21 Bukit Batok Crescent<br />#02-75 WCEGA Tower<br />Singapore 658065<br />Tel: +65 65651939<br />www.united-personnel.com<br /><br />EA Licence Number: 05C5278<br />Registration No.: R1103477<br /><br />(All applications will be treated in strictest confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates would be notified)</p>",
